# ============================================================================
# DEPLOYMENT GUIDE: Environment Variables
# ============================================================================
# This app supports TWO deployment modes:
# 1. Replit (uses Replit AI Integrations - no personal API key needed)
# 2. External (Vercel + Render - requires your own OpenAI API key)
# ============================================================================

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# FOR REPLIT DEPLOYMENT (Current Setup)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# These variables are automatically set by Replit AI Integrations.
# DO NOT modify or delete these - they're managed by Replit:
#
# AI_INTEGRATIONS_OPENAI_BASE_URL=http://localhost:1106/modelfarm/openai
# AI_INTEGRATIONS_OPENAI_API_KEY=_DUMMY_API_KEY_
#
# ✅ You're already set up! Just click "Deploy" in Replit.
# ✅ AI features will be billed to your Replit credits (no OpenAI account needed)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# FOR EXTERNAL DEPLOYMENT (Vercel + Render)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The Replit AI Integration keys above DON'T work outside Replit.
# For external deployment, you MUST set your own OpenAI API key:

# Get your key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-your-actual-openai-api-key-here

# The app will automatically use OPENAI_API_KEY if AI_INTEGRATIONS_* aren't available
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GITHUB INTEGRATION (Optional but Recommended)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Without a token: 60 requests/hour
# With a token: 5,000 requests/hour
#
# Your token is already set in Replit Secrets. For external deployment, set:
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_github_personal_access_token
# 
# Get a token from: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Required scopes: public_repo (read-only access to public repositories)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DATABASE (Provided automatically by Render/Neon)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Replit provides this automatically. For Render deployment, it's auto-configured:
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:5432/database
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SERVER CONFIGURATION
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
NODE_ENV=production
PORT=5000

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SUMMARY OF WHAT YOU NEED TO SET
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 
# For Replit Deployment:
#   ✅ Nothing! Already configured with AI Integrations
#   ✅ Optional: Add GITHUB_TOKEN for higher rate limits
#
# For External Deployment (Vercel + Render):
#   ⚠️  REQUIRED: OPENAI_API_KEY (your own key)
#   ✅ Optional: GITHUB_TOKEN (for higher rate limits)
#   ✅ Auto-configured: DATABASE_URL (Render provides this)
#
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
